<span id="freeTextContainer10617005367338834988">This was a 2 star read, but the extra star was for a narrative and romance focusing on a middle aged spinster. There were so many sexist passages that made me cringe, and a few racist ones, too. I love the movie adaptation so much more than this source material. It was quaint and fun sort of story, but severely dated to the point of not being that enjoyable for me.</span>

