        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer112840617" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9947543513996424417">I feel elated! All I wanted from life was a book about people whom I liked, people with whom I could possibly identify with. I wanted to look at a character and see their admirable qualities reflected in me. This is that book.<br/>The movie is beautiful, sweet and romantic, ao I doubted the source material, especially given my recent experences. But oh, I was wrong! I should have trusted this author and this book.<br/>This story is by a woman, about women and for women. It&apos;s empowering, and it lifted the </span>
  <span id="freeText9947543513996424417" style="display:none">I feel elated! All I wanted from life was a book about people whom I liked, people with whom I could possibly identify with. I wanted to look at a character and see their admirable qualities reflected in me. This is that book.<br />The movie is beautiful, sweet and romantic, ao I doubted the source material, especially given my recent experences. But oh, I was wrong! I should have trusted this author and this book.<br />This story is by a woman, about women and for women. It's empowering, and it lifted the weight from my soul. Maybe it can be called sappy and silly, but anyone who does it to my face will encounter my wrath.<br />I'll write a more coherent review once the euphoria has worn off.</span>
  <a data-text-id="9947543513996424417" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
